  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2063770/" class="title-link">毕竟是香港</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2063770"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/weizhoushiwang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1679535-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/weizhoushiwang/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">维舟</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-06-08"
      class="main-meta">2009-06-08 10:44:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2063770_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  必须承认，这是我第一次读林奕华的书。不过在读完后，我已经在期待他的第二、第三本书了。他的书很“好看”——作为对阅读体验的描述，“好看”在意味着“行文流畅不生涩”的同时，似乎往往也表示“易懂”因而深度不足，但他的文字却有一种回味带来的深度：虽然第一遍看不难懂...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2063770/#comments">(18回应)</a>
